I suspect that Representative Cavazos'

32:48.675 --> 33:00.930
ulterior motive was to make Corpus Christi State 
University a four-year institution. At that

33:01.670 --> 33:08.719
time, it was an upper-level institution and had 
only juniors, seniors, and graduate students.

