Apparently Representative Cavazos was talking 
to the University of Texas system at the same time

33:09.830 --> 33:37.322
and had been promised through that system's 
chairman of the Board of Regents that he would see

33:09.830 --> 33:37.322
to it that a new institution was created in South 
Texas to alleviate the lack of higher education in

